name: Wearing Cow Print
description:
Get early access to build and test build, be able to try all epochs and test them by yourself on Patreon or contact me for support on Discord

To support me you can buy me a coffe at https://ko-fi.com/antonioriolo

Training settings:

33 images, 20 steps, 14 epochs, you find many epochs (with test images using plot xy script) on my Patreon while supporting me.


Recommended settings:

  • Make sure you are aware on the usage instructions of LORA

  • Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras (Recommended for best quality, you may try other samplers)

  • CFG Scale : 5 to 9

  • LORA weight for txt2img: reccomended 0.2-0.4.

  • Keys: wearing cow print, elegant, lingerie.

I did 14 epochs, but the best one is the 1st one, wearing_cow_print01. All images posted are from this epoch because from plot xy after that it start to give cow print to everything, even the skin, so this model actually gave best result with only 20 steps each image, really rare.

i tryied to insert keyword back view but the truth it's that i didn't find enough images in cow print for a back view, so it doesn't work usually, you might try to give an higher weight to back view and hope it works.

Advices: 

1. try to move the keyword "wearing cow print" to the top if it doesn't generate cow print, try to give it a weight. In the opposite side, if everything has cow print and you want only the dress move it on the bottom and/or lower the weight on the keyword.

2. if you want to use keywords lingerie or elegant, try to use them like this "wearing elegant cow print dress" or "wearing cow print lingerie". but remember for the elegant part you need a proper environment in the prompt for a elegant dress, like a gala premier or anything where usually you wear elegant dress, bucause most of the images in the training are lingerie cow print.

3. you can decide to use other colors then white and black, in that case try to rephrase like "wearing elegant red and white cow print dress".

Enjoy!

If you'd like to support my efforts and have access to early and bleeding edge builds, please think about joining my Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/betterCuteAsians
